        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Lessening Addiction By Enhancing Labeling Opioids Act of 2019 or the LABEL Opioids Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires prescription opioids to contain a warning label specifying that the opioids may cause dependence, addiction, and overdose.</p>]]></text>
